{
  "stem": "9878.1",
  "chunk_idx": 6,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 7.8,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "But I, as a child, I knew that I went to school.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "I was a very good student at school.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "The school, there was no discrimination.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "All the school-- the children went together in school with the Gentile, Jewish kids together.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "Before, I was only strict in a Jewish school.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "And we studied.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "And we learned.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "We didn't have a too-long time to catch up to see what happened.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "But the, the war started in 1941.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "My father was able to continue work in the brewery.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And he got paid for the year that he worked in the brewery without, without getting a vacation.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "So the Russian government had forced the owners of the brewery-- whatever the money they had, they should pay out a, a month of cash because of the years that passed that my father worked in the brewery for 25 years, he didn't get paid.",
      "word_count": 45
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "So he should at least get paid for the holiday-- for the vacation days.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So we, we, we got a little money.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "My-- we bought a cow.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Then we bought another cow.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "The life was a little bit better by the Russians than by the Poles because of the compensation that my father has gotten.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "But the-- and we felt much more happier as, as Jewish kids on the street.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "The discrimination against kids were subdued because they were-- they would not allow anybody to beat somebody up because he happened to be another, another, another nationality.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Because this was-- the fear of the people were very much stronger during the Russians than the fear of the Poles.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "The Russians would not allow this, this, this kind of excesses should be committed.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "For a better life, yeah.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Financially--",
      "word_count": 1
    }
  ],
